to the family?

658
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:38,440
Being belittled for over 30 years.

659
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:40,560
Yuncheng has never complained.

660
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:42,000
He doesn't demand fairness,

661
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:43,760
but you shouldn't treat them
so differently.

662
00:38:44,160 --> 00:38:45,560
If it wasn't for being driven
to desperation this time,

663
00:38:45,560 --> 00:38:47,360
Yuncheng wouldn't have
said those things.

664
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:50,000
Even if you don't care for him,

665
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:51,840
You shouldn't push him down a dead end.

666
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:53,680
What have I wrongly accused him of?

667
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:56,000
I don't criticize him
for not being a skilled doctor.

668
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:57,480
But it's his basic human traits

669
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:58,240
that are problematic now.

670
00:38:58,600 --> 00:38:59,560
Yuncheng has already said

671
00:38:59,560 --> 00:39:01,200
that is a legitimate business strategy.

672
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,920
You think it's a problem
with his character.

673
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:05,440
Business strategy?

674
00:39:06,240 --> 00:39:07,640
I've seen it all.

675
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:09,400
With a mother like you who can't
distinguish between right and wrong,

676
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:12,320
he could only have been brought up
with moral corruption.

677
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:13,960
How am I wrong in distinguishing
between right and wrong?

678
00:39:15,040 --> 00:39:17,480
I think you don't want Yuncheng
as your son anymore.

679
00:39:18,080 --> 00:39:18,880
Fine.

680
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:21,120
Then I'll leave too.

681
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:26,480
No matter
how outstanding Gu Yunzheng is,

682
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:28,160
his surname is Gu, not Du.

683
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:31,040
He's a member of the Du family,

684
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:33,600
but he's dating a girl with chorea.

685
00:39:33,600 --> 00:39:35,560
He can't leave any lineage
for the Du family.

686
00:39:38,120 --> 00:39:38,920
What did you say?

687
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:41,680
Who is he dating?

688
00:39:42,080 --> 00:39:44,480
Looks like you're so absorbed
in your hospital duties.

689
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:46,920
Go ask around yourself.

690
00:39:49,160 --> 00:39:50,680
Tell me the truth!

691
00:39:55,840 --> 00:39:57,440
You're out of your mind.

692
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,400
She has chorea.

693
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:00,840
And because of her,

694
00:40:01,120 --> 00:40:02,720
