695
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:04,880
Is this how you regard your career?

696
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,120
I'm not out of my mind.

697
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:08,160
I didn't do it
on the spur of the moment.

698
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:10,480
I have a detailed plan for my project.

699
00:40:10,840 --> 00:40:13,120
